title: Group Therapy: He's Wants a $6500 Putting Green
description: A quick update from the Emergency Group Therapy we had last week about the sister that was meeting up with a guy in Puerto Rico.  Then we dive into another Group Therapy about a woman who's husband wants to put in a putting green in their backyard.
